description:
&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited for the post of Consultant Cardiologist with a special interest in coronary intervention at Queen Alexandra Hospital, Portsmouth. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for two dynamic and enthusiastic colleagues to help drive forward the PCI service, to help sustain the primary PCI service and to take a share in the management of acute cardiac admissions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates must hold a CCT in cardiology as well as being fully trained and independent in performing PCI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details, or to arrange an informal visit, please contact Alex Hobson on 02392 286000 or via email at alex.hobson@porthosp.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing date: &lt;/strong&gt;Sunday 22nd November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interview date: &lt;/strong&gt;Friday 11th December 2020&lt;/p&gt;
